<div class="form_wrapper wrapper_padding">
  <h1>Interested in getting a jumpstart on your future career today? Join the TTM Writer Community.</h1>
  <p>Here at The Teen Magazine, we are a close-knit group of young college and high school writers who work closely with one another to improve journalism skills,
    gain writing experience, and receive quality feedback from top-tier student journalists. Here is a video of TTM's founder and Editor in Chief explaining who we are a bit more!</p>
    <iframe width="560" height="315" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/9dsKTqtu1bw" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen></iframe>
<br />
<h1>What Does it Mean to be a Writer for The Teen Magazine?</h1>
<p>As a writer for The Teen Magazine, you will get the opportunity to:  </p>
<ul>
  <li>Pitch article topics and get published in an international online magazine</li>
  <li>Have your own public author page that you can share with potential employers</li>
  <li>Gain applicable experience and training in the editorial industry</li>
  <li>Be paired with a mentor who can give you feedback and guidance</li>
  <li>Interview successful people and work with brands</li>
  <li>Learn from and network with our talented writer community</li>
  <li>Apply for other positions and internships within The Teen Magazine</li>
</ul>
  <h1>Convinced? Apply now.</h1>
  <p>Because we only have a limited number of openings per month, please be thoughtful in your application and explain exactly why you would really love to write for The Teen Magazine. We canâ€™t wait to read your submission!</p>
  <%= form_for @application do |f| %>
    <span>First Name</span>
    <%= f.text_field :first_name, required: true %>
    <br />
    <span>Last Name</span>
    <%= f.text_field :last_name, required: true %>
    <br />
    <span>Email</span>
    <%= f.email_field :email, required: true %>
    <br />
    <span>Primary Category</span><br /><br />
    <%= f.select :category, ['Academics', 'Beauty', 'DIY', 'Entertainment', 'Fashion', 'Get Involved', 'Health & Fitness', 'Lifestyle', 'News', 'Tips & Hacks']%><br />
    <br />
    <br />
    <span>Please write a one-page cover letter introducing yourself and describing why you would be a good fit for The Teen Magazine. Please include links to any previously published work/blog if applicable.
    </span>
    <%= f.text_area :description, required: true %>
    <br />
    <div class="hidden">
      <%= f.label :nickname %> <br />
      <%= f.text_field :nickname %>
    </div>
    <span>
      Applications are accepted on a rolling basis. If accepted, you will receive an email from our team of editors within 48 hours.
    </span><br /><br />
    <%= f.submit 'Submit Application' %>
  <% end %>
  <br>
  <br>
</div>
